nodes.text: Defender Squadron One, or simply Defender Squadron, was a starfighter squadron in the Galactic Empire's Seventh Fleet. It was made up of twelve TIE/d "Defender" Multi-Role Starfighters and its commander was Captain Vult Skerris until his death during the Lothal campaign, in which Skerris used a TIE/D Defender Elite. Captain Benj Dobbs led the squadron after the death of Captain Skerris.
